yTime":"2018-11-16T01:08:56.000Z","msg":"咁你出一出街咪成日扯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4044f9d61bde4d875b275c774b678f435985343c","tid":903822,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"393316c4f31de7793bcddf9ccf801ee4ae963f85","tid":903822,"uid":146063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:04:08.000Z","msg":"隨口講下架炸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"我相信佢唔會咁樣呃我地呢啲漁民"},{"pid":"722850a8d6af7622627ff7571b10dc4df9d8e0af","tid":903822,"uid":1159,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:13:29.000Z","msg":"G.E.M. 鄧紫棋，1991年8月16日在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上海出生</span></strong><br />\n於2008年出道<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2013年</span></strong><br />\n發生 鄧紫棋撰文支持梁振英事件，在香港集思會的《90後有話說&hellip;》特集中，她表示：<br />\n<em>我想跟梁振英說句「加油」呀！</em><br />\n<br />\n而當時她剃頭以塑造一個punk的形象，但卻不懂punk的反建制精神，是為<strong>言行不一</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZLw8AY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZLw8AY.png&h=0a231a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NyqAQPj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyqAQPj.png&h=52e6731c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uTS3ZHE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuTS3ZHE.png&h=dfb0e2ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E6VtrnF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE6VtrnF.png&h=5ef70dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2014年</span></strong><br />\n參加中國湖南衛視《我是歌手》爆紅 ，最終得到亞軍。當時<strong>被網民指不如留在家鄉發展</strong>。<br />\n而她更一朝得志，語無倫次 ，<strong>與金秀賢等人傳緋聞</strong>。甚至連中國網民都開始對鄧有反響。她亦甚至聲言上太空<strong>代表中國唱歌</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n而她指香港樂壇要「砍掉重練」，但與此同時連中國都聲言封殺。<br />\n9月尾正值雨傘革命期間，警方施放催淚彈清場。她在這時卻發放了一張開心照片，說：「禮拜六啦！明天又一個新開始！大家周末在幹嘛？」結果立即受到不少香港網民狂轟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UdLEx2G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdLEx2G.png&h=11b600ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teBgAf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteBgAf1.png&h=7aed8452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/faf5tA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffaf5tA2.png&h=e0a83392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nXkMXun.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnXkMXun.png&h=ad66ec32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DaxrXuo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDaxrXuo.png&h=3e6729fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TnP6c2K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnP6c2K.png&h=50d57c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2015年</span></strong><br />\n香港演唱會最貴門票盛惠$1880 ，被揶揄為<strong>國際G.E.M.、太空G.E.M.</strong>。而因長期在中國發展關係，<strong>連廣東話發音都開始出現偏差</strong>。<br />\n而演唱會採訪安排亦<strong>優待中國傳媒</strong>，香港傳媒只有報章攝影師可以入場拍攝首30分鐘。而<strong>中國傳媒則獲安排座位採訪拍攝以及會後近距離做訪問，更來回機票酒店全包。</strong><br />\n傳被中國被封殺，但又說飲水思源，企圖修補與香港關係。<br />\n因在中國長時間工作，連衣著品味也開始走向強國大媽Look。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGwoZHK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwGwoZHK.png&h=4b0a5110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNZFhuq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNZFhuq.png&h=a75f7ad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/meQ5tA6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmeQ5tA6.png&h=8bd2b398&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1pBAf6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1pBAf6.png&h=78d9b5d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BRMc2N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BRMc2N.png&h=95b8cb11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而她今日雖然仍自稱香港歌手，但廣東歌的產量已大不如前，<strong>在2015年的唱片中更完全沒有廣東歌</strong><br />\n(歌曲總數 / 廣東歌數量 / 百分比)<br />\n2008年 - G.E.M. (5 / 3 / 60%)<br />\n2009年 - 18... (12 / 5 / 42%)<br />\n2010年 - MySecret (10 / 3 / 30%)<br />\n2011年 - Xposed (10 / 3 / 30%)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2015年 - 新的心跳 (10 / 0 / 0%)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，G.E.M. 曾自己填詞一曲<em>What Have U Done</em>，而她自己卻成為了這首歌的反面教材，實在諷刺。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6_X9CZI8xRs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6_X9CZI8xRs&d=MpvUtDhoU6d9xR18VsuFQ4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=dec70a85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6_X9CZI8xRs</a>"},{"pid":"c8b8589adcd85afb8ed6719596417c9cda786772","tid":903822,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8716d25f5e9210813e3e201bb6ce1893c83ba0","tid":903822,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:04:25.000Z","msg":"坐佢隔黎同佢傾計應該會全程忍唔住扯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:15:37.000Z","msg":"我就咁睇都扯扯地啦..."},{"pid":"35ec7251ece3d8a7724f5f5ae5a489e05f027f61","tid":903822,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9cd2b5fe8cbf6a93e12220561c8bf6b87a1f22c","tid":903822,"uid":96859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:06:20.000Z","msg":"可能只係初步協議咗呢件事 未必真係11月搞 就算搞都未咁快出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:30:32.000Z","msg":"寧願遲出好過無"},{"pid":"5eed14cbf59a26856591d25d311850f74245a545","tid":903822,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8b8589adcd85afb8ed6719596417c9cda786772","tid":903822,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8716d25f5e9210813e3e201bb6ce1893c83b